ght glow in darkness. Raichu plants its tail in the ground to discharge electricity."},{"version":"sun","text":"It unleashes electric shocks that can reach 100,000 volts. When agitated, it can knock out even an Indian elephant."},{"version":"moon","text":"It becomes aggressive when it has electricity stored up. At such times, even its Trainer has to take care to avoid being attacked."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"As electricity builds up inside its body, it becomes more aggressive. One theory is that the electricity buildup is actually causing stress."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Because so many Trainers like the way Pikachu looks, you don\u2019t see this Pok\u00e9mon very often."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"When electricity builds up inside its body, it becomes feisty. It also glows in the dark."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"When electricity builds up inside its body, it becomes feisty. It also glows in the dark."},{"version":"shield","text":"If its electric pouches run empty, it raises its tail to gather electricity from the atmosphere."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"It can discharge bursts of electricity exceeding 100,000 volts\u2014 a single strike with that amount of power would incapacitate one of the Copperajah of my homeland."}],"evo":{"name":"pichu","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"pikachu","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":220,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"raichu","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"thunder-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":